OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778681476
OL,3,CExplosive chemicals discovered not
OL,4,Cbeing treated as terror related,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,FA chemical substance incident which
OL,8,Fsparked a major emergency response in
OL,9,FManchester's Gay Village is not being
OL,10,Ftreated as terror-related, police have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FOne man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fmaking an explosive device after the
OL,15,Fchemical substances were uncovered in
OL,16,Fa hotel room on Canal Street yesterday
OL,17,F(May 11). The hotel was evacuated as
OL,18,Fthe chemicals and 'items' within the
OL,19,Froom were assessed by specialists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
