PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778681476
OL,3,CExplosive chemicals discovered not
OL,4,Cbeing treated as terror related,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,FIn an update issued this morning
OL,8,F(Tuesday) a spokesperson for Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police said the incident
OL,10,Fwas not believed to be terror-related.
OL,11,FThe arrested man remains in custody
OL,12,Fthis morning for questioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
