OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778681476
OL,3,CExplosive chemicals discovered not
OL,4,Cbeing treated as terror related,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,FEmergency crews descended on Canal
OL,8,FStreet yesterday morning after members
OL,9,Fof the public reported a 'chemical'
OL,10,Fsmell to police. A large cordon was
OL,11,Fput in place on a stretch of the
OL,12,Fusually bustling street between the
OL,13,Fjunctions of Sackville Street and
OL,14,FRichmond Street and the hotel was
OL,15,Fevacuated.
OL,17,FA number of nearby bars and pubs were
OL,18,Falso evacuated. A large number of
OL,19,Fpolice officers and firefighters were
OL,20,Fpictured within the cordon, which was
OL,21,Feventually reduced at around 4pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
