OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778681476
OL,3,CExplosive chemicals discovered not
OL,4,Cbeing treated as terror related,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,FPolice said the chemical substances
OL,8,Ffound in the room were 'examined' and
OL,9,Fwere last night in the 'process of
OL,10,Fbeing safely removed'. A GMP
OL,11,Fspokesperson said the examination of
OL,12,Fthe chemicals 'ruled out any explosive
OL,13,Frisk'.
OL,15,FNobody was injured amid the incident.
OL,16,FDetectives could be seen going in and
OL,17,Fout of businesses along the street
OL,18,Fwhile white-clad forensics officers
OL,19,Fphotographed the scene and specialised
OL,20,Fteams examined the material.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
